      "created": "2013-06-07T17:56:02.612+0000",
      "description": "At present we are sending bunch of information mainly related to auxiliary serivces to whoever launches the container. This is an added overhead for NM. Instead we can expose this as an API then using NMToken client can get this information whenever it needs it.",
